haar cascades practica

## Env backend
FACE_CASCADE_PATH=docs/haarcascade_frontalface_alt.xml
EYES_CASCADE_PATH=docs/haarcascade_eye_tree_eyeglasses.xml
CAMERA_INDEX=0

## Env frontend
Copy `frontend/.env.local.example` to `frontend/.env.local`.

## Run backend API
cd backend && task install && task api

## Run frontend
cd frontend && npm install && npm run dev

Open http://localhost:3000 and allow camera access.
Frontend sends frames via WebSocket endpoint `ws://localhost:8000/ws/detect`.

## Optional desktop mode (legacy)
cd backend && task run

link for dataset https://github.com/opencv/opencv/blob/master/data/haarcascades/haarcascade_frontalface_default.xml
lint for dataset https://github.com/opencv/opencv/blob/master/data/haarcascades/haarcascade_eye_tree_eyeglasses.xml
linl for dataset https://github.com/opencv/opencv/blob/master/data/haarcascades/haarcascade_frontalface_alt.xml

